00:41.833 --> 00:45.250
I guess to tell the story
of the Good Friday murder through my eyes,

00:45.333 --> 00:46.958
I got to start here.

00:47.625 --> 00:51.750
Nine months ago, when this asshole deacon
said something way out of line,

00:51.833 --> 00:53.041
and I did this.

00:58.333 --> 00:59.958
Oh, shit.

01:00.750 --> 01:03.083
So, you're a fighter, then?

01:03.583 --> 01:05.708
Uh, no, Father, absolutely not.

01:05.791 --> 01:09.041
Well, we have a deacon who would say
otherwise if his jaw wasn't broken.

01:09.125 --> 01:11.750
In my previous life, yes, I was a boxer,

01:12.250 --> 01:14.833
and I lived on the streets.
I did some other things.

01:14.916 --> 01:18.708
We need fighters today,
but to fight the world,

01:19.458 --> 01:21.083
not ourselves.

01:21.166 --> 01:24.625
A priest is a shepherd.
The world is a wolf.

01:24.708 --> 01:25.833
No.

01:29.250 --> 01:33.625
I… I don't believe that,
Father, respectfully.

01:33.708 --> 01:36.500
You start fighting wolves,
and before you know it,

01:36.583 --> 01:38.291
everyone you don't understand is a wolf.

01:39.333 --> 01:42.333
I still got that fighting instinct,
and I gave into it today,

01:42.416 --> 01:44.833
but Christ came to heal the world,
not fight it.

01:44.916 --> 01:46.208
I believe that.

01:46.291 --> 01:49.583
It's this, not this, you know?

01:50.833 --> 01:52.666
I just want to be a good priest.

01:53.625 --> 01:56.916
Show broken people like me
the forgiveness and love of Christ.

01:57.000 --> 01:59.000
The world needs that so bad.

02:01.708 --> 02:04.583
You give me one more shot,
and I promise I'll do that.

02:16.958 --> 02:18.125
Your Excellency,

02:18.833 --> 02:21.041
you stuck your neck out for me
so many times.

02:21.125 --> 02:23.625
-I let you down, and whatever the--
-All right.

02:23.708 --> 02:24.791
Listen…

02:25.291 --> 02:28.250
Deacon Clark is famously a dick.

02:28.333 --> 02:30.791
Nobody's actually that upset
that you clocked him.

02:30.875 --> 02:32.375
In fact, kind of the opposite.

02:32.458 --> 02:35.041
But we do need to do something about it.

02:36.041 --> 02:39.250
We're sending you
to a small parish in Chimney Rock.

02:39.333 --> 02:42.375
It's just one priest there now.

02:43.666 --> 02:45.000
Assistant pastor?

02:45.083 --> 02:47.250
Yeah, well, curb your enthusiasm.

02:47.333 --> 02:48.166
What?

02:48.666 --> 02:53.416
You're going
to Our Lady of Perpetual Fortitude,

02:53.500 --> 02:56.583
led by Monsignor Jefferson Wicks.
Have you heard of Jefferson Wicks?

02:57.458 --> 03:00.958
Okay, look, Wicks has his supporters here.
I'm not one of them.

03:01.041 --> 03:02.125
Between you and me,

03:02.208 --> 03:05.166
I think he's a few beads shy of
a full rosary and a real son of a bitch.

03:06.166 --> 03:10.833
But what's undeniable is that his flock
is shrinking and even calcifying.

03:11.791 --> 03:15.333
It could use some of what
you said in there. You understand?

03:15.958 --> 03:18.291
Not at all, but yes.

03:18.375 --> 03:20.458
Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.

03:20.541 --> 03:23.416
-Spirit's got me. Let me at him.
-Hey. Hey, hey.

03:23.500 --> 03:27.041
This, not this, right? Mm?

03:31.166 --> 03:32.375
Good luck, kid.

03:38.166 --> 03:40.791
So, that's how I came to Chimney Rock.

03:43.333 --> 03:45.166
Daniel in the lion's den.

03:45.250 --> 03:47.000
David facing off Goliath.

03:47.500 --> 03:49.916
Young, dumb, and full of Christ.

03:50.000 --> 03:51.750
Ready for anything.

04:23.791 --> 04:24.875
Father Jefferson?

04:25.791 --> 04:28.083
Hello. Jud Duplenticy from Albany?

04:28.166 --> 04:30.875
Lord be with you,
Jud Duplenticy from Albany.

04:34.000 --> 04:36.125
You here to take my church away from me?

04:37.458 --> 04:39.250
Oh. No.

04:39.833 --> 04:40.708
Good.

04:41.583 --> 04:44.000
Okay, call me Monsignor Wicks.

04:44.916 --> 04:46.208
I see you've met Martha.

04:47.083 --> 04:48.333
Martha? No.

04:48.416 --> 04:49.916
-Monsignor Wicks.
-Jesus!

04:50.000 --> 04:52.500
I woke up early to polish the silver.

04:52.583 --> 04:53.875
It was a bit blotchy.

04:53.958 --> 04:55.500
That'll be fine, Martha.

04:55.583 --> 04:57.791
Father… Jud.

04:59.083 --> 05:00.375
You are welcome here.

05:00.875 --> 05:02.500
-Thank you, Martha.
-Mm.

05:02.583 --> 05:05.208
I was actually
just saying to Father Wicks…

05:05.291 --> 05:06.875
Monsignor Wicks.

05:07.708 --> 05:09.583
Monsignor, right. Sorry.

05:10.083 --> 05:11.708
And sorry for saying "Jesus".

05:13.500 --> 05:15.666
Hoo. This is going great, I think.

05:15.750 --> 05:18.291
-Bishop Langstrom sent you, huh?
-Mm-hmm.

05:19.166 --> 05:20.250
Langstrom.

05:20.750 --> 05:22.416
I know him well.

05:22.500 --> 05:24.708
He handpicked you, sent you here.

05:25.500 --> 05:27.000
It says something to me.

05:29.583 --> 05:30.791
Tells me a lot.

05:31.916 --> 05:34.708
Well, I… I know
you're used to flying solo, but, um…

05:35.291 --> 05:36.916
I'm… I'm here to serve.

05:38.416 --> 05:39.625
Take my confession.

05:41.291 --> 05:43.083
All right.

05:43.791 --> 05:45.083
Mm.

05:47.166 --> 05:49.708
Bless me, Father, for I have sinned.

05:49.791 --> 05:51.000
It's been, uh,

05:51.875 --> 05:54.291
six weeks since my last confession.

05:58.708 --> 06:01.250
I've envied the material wealth of others.

06:02.125 --> 06:06.750
I saw this luxury car commercial.
Sam had it on his TV. Lexus.

06:07.416 --> 06:08.625
And I thought,

06:09.125 --> 06:11.875
"Ah! That is a good-looking car."

06:11.958 --> 06:13.458
The coupe.

06:14.583 --> 06:17.958
Uh… I've envied the power of great men.

06:19.375 --> 06:22.750
Envied my grandfather's power as a priest.
I wanted that.

06:22.833 --> 06:24.041
Always did.

06:25.791 --> 06:26.791
Uh…

06:27.541 --> 06:28.958
I've masturbated,

06:30.166 --> 06:33.708
um, four times this week.

06:33.791 --> 06:36.625
Four or five, generally, in…
What'd I say, six weeks?

06:36.708 --> 06:39.791
Well, let's say 30 times, masturbated.

06:40.833 --> 06:44.458
Uh, this week, in my bed,
in the morning once.

06:44.958 --> 06:49.041
Once in the shower, standing up,
which was convenient.

06:49.125 --> 06:51.250
Just use a bath gel.

06:52.333 --> 06:55.541
Oh, once in the middle of the night,
after a dream about--

06:55.625 --> 06:58.208
-That's all right.
-About one of those Japanese cat cafés.

06:58.291 --> 07:00.625
-Okay.
-You know, I read this article,

07:00.708 --> 07:05.916
but the cats were girls,
and, you know, so…

07:06.583 --> 07:08.000
And I hadn't prepared,

07:08.083 --> 07:12.125
so I had to finish into a copy
of Catholic Chronicle magazine,

07:12.833 --> 07:16.916
just what was on the end table,
which is probably its own kind of sin.

07:17.416 --> 07:20.416
I don't know, maybe not, but… Not good.

07:21.541 --> 07:23.833
At the time,
I thought this was just weird.

07:24.833 --> 07:26.916
But looking back now, I know.

07:27.000 --> 07:29.333
This was Wicks' first punch.

07:29.416 --> 07:31.458
Five Hail Marys and one Glory Be.

07:33.166 --> 07:34.458
Thank you, Father.

07:40.041 --> 07:41.541
It wouldn't be his last.

07:41.625 --> 07:42.875
Oh, and welcome

07:43.666 --> 07:45.083
to my church.

07:48.750 --> 07:51.208
Over the next few weeks, I settled in

07:51.291 --> 07:53.500
at Our Lady of Perpetual Fortitude.

07:59.166 --> 08:03.791
The only other full-time employee
was the groundskeeper, Samson.

08:04.500 --> 08:05.583
Sam.

08:11.125 --> 08:12.833
It's Monsignor Wicks

08:12.916 --> 08:17.000
who gives me the strength every day
to not go back to the bottle.

08:17.916 --> 08:19.041
He used to drink too.

08:20.125 --> 08:24.083
But he said to me once,
"If I can stave off that demon, you can."

08:25.375 --> 08:27.291
And every day, it is a struggle.

08:28.166 --> 08:29.250
But I have.

08:30.541 --> 08:34.041
I credit him and… my sweet Martha.

08:34.125 --> 08:36.625
Your… your sweet Martha?

08:36.708 --> 08:38.333
I'd do anything for her.

08:39.708 --> 08:42.083
My angel on Earth.

08:42.166 --> 08:45.458
As far as the church goes,
Martha does it all.

08:45.541 --> 08:48.750
She keeps the books,
manages donations, files everything.

08:48.833 --> 08:49.958
File that.

08:50.541 --> 08:52.958
She launders the vestments,
stocks the supplies,

08:53.041 --> 08:55.166
feeds Wicks, plays the organ.

08:58.875 --> 09:00.791
She knew where the bodies were buried.

09:01.583 --> 09:03.666
-So this is the crypt?
-Yep.

09:03.750 --> 09:06.708
It's a damn shame.
Gotta put up a security camera.

09:07.208 --> 09:09.333
-Is there an entrance?
-There is.

09:10.500 --> 09:11.708
This right here,

09:12.208 --> 09:13.333
it's a Lazarus door.

09:14.041 --> 09:16.916
Takes construction equipment
to open from the outside.

09:17.000 --> 09:19.875
But cantilevered as such that one push

09:20.458 --> 09:22.875
will send it tumbling
to the ground from inside.

09:24.125 --> 09:25.458
Who's in there then?

09:25.541 --> 09:26.541
Prentice.

09:27.166 --> 09:30.625
Wicks' grandfather,
the founder of this church.

09:31.500 --> 09:33.000
Was like a father to me.

09:33.666 --> 09:35.666
Makes me sick.

09:35.750 --> 09:40.000
These kids painting rocket ships
all over his sacred resting place.

09:46.708 --> 09:49.416
-What are you doing?
-Oh, uh…

09:50.208 --> 09:52.125
Well, I do a little wood-working,

09:52.208 --> 09:55.708
so thought I could borrow
some of Sam's tools, make a proper--

09:55.791 --> 09:57.000
No, we leave that.

09:57.083 --> 09:59.958
A reminder of the shameful sin
of the harlot whore.

10:01.500 --> 10:02.916
Take my confession.

10:04.875 --> 10:06.625
Yes, the harlot whore.

10:08.125 --> 10:09.625
That was Wicks' mother.

10:09.708 --> 10:12.333
Okay, so what's the deal with that?

10:12.416 --> 10:14.625
She was a harlot and a whore.

10:15.458 --> 10:16.291
Okay.

10:16.375 --> 10:19.583
When Prentice entered the priesthood
and founded this church,

10:19.666 --> 10:21.833
he was widowed with a daughter.

10:22.958 --> 10:24.541
Grace was her name.

10:25.125 --> 10:26.750
Always a bad seed.

10:26.833 --> 10:32.166
She loved revealing clothes
and her fancy brands.

10:32.250 --> 10:33.875
Fancy brands… Oof.

10:33.958 --> 10:35.041
-Mm.
-Yeah.

10:35.125 --> 10:37.958
As a teenager, she slutted around bars,

10:38.041 --> 10:40.250
was soon pregnant by a drifter.

10:41.250 --> 10:45.291
Prentice had
a vast family fortune in the bank.

10:45.375 --> 10:48.416
To protect his grandson, Wicks,

10:48.500 --> 10:53.083
he promised that
if Grace stayed under his roof,

10:53.791 --> 10:56.916
the fortune would be willed to her.

10:57.916 --> 11:01.750
And so the whore
waited for her father to die.

11:02.666 --> 11:05.083
Oh, it weighed on him heavily.

11:05.166 --> 11:06.666
Martha, remember this.

11:07.833 --> 11:10.666
Wealth and the power that comes with it,

11:11.416 --> 11:12.666
is Eve's Apple.

11:13.916 --> 11:16.041
Temptation that leads to the fall.

11:17.291 --> 11:21.125
I must protect our loved ones
from its corrupting influence,

11:22.208 --> 11:23.625
at all costs.

11:24.375 --> 11:26.208
His day came at last.

11:26.291 --> 11:27.541
I was there.

11:28.625 --> 11:31.833
I saw Prentice take his final communion

11:31.916 --> 11:34.666
and die on the holy altar.

11:34.750 --> 11:36.166
At peace.

11:36.958 --> 11:40.458
The harlot whore
went straight to Prentice's attorney.

11:41.041 --> 11:44.125
"Give me my money," she said.

11:45.375 --> 11:46.833
And do you know what he said?

11:47.958 --> 11:52.458
"Yes, you are heir
to every single penny Prentice had."

11:53.250 --> 11:54.875
And in his accounts,

11:56.166 --> 11:59.166
not one hot dime.

11:59.875 --> 12:02.041
Mm, what did he do with the fortune?

12:02.125 --> 12:04.041
Gave it to the poor, say some.

12:04.666 --> 12:07.541
Threw it in the ocean, say others.
No one knows.

12:08.416 --> 12:09.416
It was gone.

12:10.375 --> 12:14.208
That holy man's final act of grace

12:15.333 --> 12:19.625
was to keep the corrupting evil
out of wicked hands.

12:20.666 --> 12:22.500
All that he left her…

12:25.541 --> 12:26.541
was this.

12:27.166 --> 12:29.208
"What is this?" she said.

12:30.291 --> 12:31.708
But I knew.

12:32.416 --> 12:34.250
Look not for Eve's Apple.

12:34.916 --> 12:38.333
Your inheritance is now Christ.

12:44.208 --> 12:46.833
That night, she had her revenge.

12:50.000 --> 12:52.000
In a demonic rage,

12:52.083 --> 12:56.166
