13:11.416 --> 13:13.833
Blasphemy, desecration.

13:15.416 --> 13:18.416
Evil incarnate.

13:54.083 --> 13:56.458
I said, "Sister Grace,

13:56.541 --> 14:01.458
God, your Father,
will forgive you in His love."

14:18.041 --> 14:19.541
She died,

14:20.083 --> 14:22.375
throwing herself against Prentice's tomb.

14:25.541 --> 14:27.541
Brain aneurysm, they said.

14:28.750 --> 14:30.666
Struck down, I say,

14:31.541 --> 14:34.875
by God in His mercy.

14:35.958 --> 14:37.500
Holy shit.

14:39.666 --> 14:40.666
Sorry, sorry.

14:43.000 --> 14:46.333
The darkness of that story
was the bedrock of this place.

14:46.416 --> 14:48.666
You could feel it.

14:48.750 --> 14:50.083
And he asked, "Who told you…"

14:50.166 --> 14:54.500
