16:11.833 --> 16:14.416
I've given up a lot to…

16:14.500 --> 16:19.041
…be loyal to my dad
and to Cy and to Wicks.

16:20.375 --> 16:21.708
So I think that

16:21.791 --> 16:25.208
when my dad
is looking down on me from heaven,

16:25.291 --> 16:28.708
I think he is very…

16:28.791 --> 16:30.500
…pleased with me.

16:32.875 --> 16:34.291
So I guess that's nice.

16:34.958 --> 16:36.041
I came this close.

16:36.125 --> 16:38.666
I was the GOP golden boy, the great hope.

16:38.750 --> 16:41.291
I've got connections and ins and outs.

16:41.375 --> 16:43.500
I was on the cusp,
but I just couldn't engage voters.

16:43.583 --> 16:47.500
I didn't… have that
cult of personality thing, I guess.

16:47.583 --> 16:50.416
It's hard connecting with people
in a genuine way.

16:50.500 --> 16:52.208
-I know.
-Mm-hmm.

16:52.291 --> 16:54.708
I tried everything. Believe me,
I hammered the race thing.

16:54.791 --> 16:57.000
I hammered the gender thing,
the trans thing,

16:57.083 --> 16:59.208
the border thing, the homeless thing,

16:59.291 --> 17:03.125
the war thing, the election thing,
the abortion thing, the climate thing.

17:03.916 --> 17:07.916
Thing about induction stoves,
Israel, library books, vaccines,

17:08.000 --> 17:11.083
