17:44.291 --> 17:45.958
She was his everything.

17:46.041 --> 17:47.875
Darla left me last week.

17:47.958 --> 17:49.625
Oh, I'm sorry.

17:50.125 --> 17:53.000
Took the kids, moved to Tucson

17:54.166 --> 17:56.791
with some guy that she met
on a Phish message board.

18:00.416 --> 18:01.625
Phish the band?

18:01.708 --> 18:03.125
