"Wicks. Be careful,

19:28.083 --> 19:32.166
you gotta shake him off.
He's bad news. Opportunistic poetaster."

19:33.166 --> 19:36.791
We're gonna have to protect Wicks
from these leeching millennials.

19:36.875 --> 19:39.666
Simone was new to town,
and new to the church.

19:39.750 --> 19:43.291
