20:24.416 --> 20:26.833
Faith in God to heal me.

20:29.041 --> 20:30.250
This is different.

20:33.625 --> 20:36.250
I feel hopeful now.

20:38.125 --> 20:40.416
Like a miracle could happen.

20:43.500 --> 20:45.916
That's how Monsignor Wicks makes me feel.

20:56.791 --> 20:59.708
The Spirit really moved him today, huh?

21:00.958 --> 21:02.166
Monsignor!

21:03.083 --> 21:04.333
Ah, my warrior.

21:04.916 --> 21:08.000
